    sourceTier: "ai_assisted",
    sourceNotes: "Narrative unit synthesized from Hosea 1-3. Historical context drawn from Assyrian-period archaeology and ANE marriage law. Interpretive framework informed by Abraham Heschel's 'The Prophets' and Francis Andersen/David Noel Freedman's Anchor Bible commentary on Hosea."
