    sourceTier: "ai_assisted",
    sourceNotes: "Narrative unit synthesized from Hosea 11:1-11. 'Pathos of God' framework drawn from Abraham Heschel. Impassibility debate informed by Terence Fretheim's 'The Suffering of God.' Assyrian historical context per ANET and Cogan/Tadmor."
